video_description:
Subscribe to Lexus: http://bit.ly/Lm4j4n 

What's the point of an EPA-estimated 42 miles per gallon* if those miles aren't interesting? 

This YouTube-exclusive 90-second extended cut version of "42 Miles" was directed by Jonas Akerlund and features Beck's remix of Lykke Li's "Get Some." To learn more about the CT, visit http://www.Lexus.com/CT or search Twitter for #LexusCT.

*Based on EPA combined mileage ratings 43/40/42 city/hwy/comb. Actual mileage will vary.

Go to our website:  http://www.lexus.com/
Find us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/lexus
Follow us on Twitter: http://twitter.com/#!/lexus 
Lexus Drivers: http://drivers.lexus.com
L Studio: http://www.youtube.com/user/lstudiopresents

About Lexus: Welcome to Lexus' official YouTube Channel, your front row seat to watching the Pursuit of Perfection.

Official Lexus CT Commercial (Extended Cut) -- "Miles"
YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/lexus
title: Lexus CT Commercial - Miles
